          private void writeObject(java.io.ObjectOutputStream ignored)
                  throws java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException
          Blocks the Java serialization mechanism.

          It is a common case for a servlet not to be able to serialize its fields. Thus, any servlet class derived from NonSerializableServlet refuses the serialization bequest.

          Throws:
          java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - always
